    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait really? i’ve read online that it’s fine as long as you don't take huge amounts at once. like, it's just a plant, right? i feel like sertraline is already doing the heavy lifting so a little bit of the herb shouldn't really mess with the chemistry that much. are you sure it's actually a \"dangerous\" condition and not just like, a slight side effect like nausea or something?",
